<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN348">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>veṇṇel lariñar taṇṇumai verīik</l>
<l>kaṇmaṭaṟ koṇṭa tīntē ṉiriyak</l>
<l>kaḷḷarik kuṅkuyañ ciṟumīṉ cīvum</l>
<l>pāṇcēri  vāymoḻit taḻumpaṉū raṉṉa</l>
<l>kuvaḷai yuṇka ṇivaḷait tāyē</l>
<l>yīṉā ḷāyiṉa ḷāyi ṉāṉātu</l>
<l>niḻaṟoṟu neṭuntēr niṟpa vayiṉṟoṟuñ</l>
<l>cennutal yāṉai piṇippa</l>
<l>varukaṉa maṉṉem peruntuṟai maraṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the village of true-worded Taḻumpaṉ with a bard’s quarter</l>
<l>where the sweep little fish [and] a potter clan who filter toddy</l>
<l>so that the sweet honey [bees] retreat who take to knotted palm fronds</l>
<l>when frightened by the Taṇṇumai drum of the cutters of white paddy,</l>
<l>she with waterlily kajal eyes, her mother,</l>
<l>if she had not given birth [to her], would</l>
<l>when without end large chariots stand in every shade,</l>
<l>when they tie elephants with red foreheads on every side,</l>
<l>they not become scarce indeed, the trees of our big harbour?  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
